      • isHangul

        public static boolean isHangul(char value)
        Check whether given character is single Hangul character or not.

        Giving ㄲ,ㅏ,ㅢ ... returns true. However return false when a,b,c,...,가,나,... is given

        Parameters:
        value - value to check
        Returns:
        true when given value is Hangul otherwise false
